Chapter 1. What you will learn

In this chapter, you will learn the following:

* How to install and configure Python and the Jupyter Notebook.
* How to read data from a CSV file into a pandas DataFrame.
* How to clean and transform data using pandas DataFrame methods.
* How to analyze data using pandas DataFrame methods.
* How to visualize data using matplotlib.
* How to publish your analysis using Jupyter.

