Chapter 3. Prologue: Prerequisites

To take this course, you will need the following:

* A computer with a recent version of Python installed.
* A web browser.
* A basic understanding of mathematics.

If you do not have Python installed, you can download it for free from the Python website.

If you do not have a web browser, you can use Google Chrome, Firefox, or Safari.

If you do not have a basic understanding of mathematics, you may want to review some basic concepts before taking this course.

